        "timestamp": "2017-10-12 12:10:03.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nUnfortunately, markdown files cannot be used directly as rst.  They need to be converted -just renaming .md to .rst won't work - that's why the verify build is failing.\n\nPandoc is a good utility for this (https://pandoc.org) ... the command line format would be something like:\npandoc -f markdown -t rst -o foo.rst foo.md",
